# ── Secrets / env ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ignore .env and ANY .env.* (local, e2e, prod, staging, …) — these hold real
# secrets, provisioned from the secret manager / locally, NEVER committed.
# Committed templates are the *.example files (placeholders only) — re-included below.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.prod.example

# Local e2e secrets: JWT private/public keys, generated tokens — never commit.
.secrets/
# Observability overlay scrape token (real token never committed).
infra/observability/secrets/scrape_token

# Defense-in-depth: never commit private keys / certs anywhere in the tree,
# even outside .secrets/. No public .pem/.key is meant to be committed by default;
# if one ever must be, add a targeted `!path/to/file` exception below.
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.cer
*.der
*.crt

# ── Python ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/

# ── IDE / editor ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea/
.vscode/

# ── Local scratch / run artifacts (not part of the repo) ────────
# Captured test/run output logs from local runs.
*_err.txt
*.log
# Figma design reference screenshots used for the gap-analysis (not backend source).
# Remove this line if you intend to version the design references.
screenshot/
# Ad-hoc screenshots pasted into the repo root during debugging (not source).
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png

# ── Agent tooling (multi-agent orchestration kitchen, not the service) ──
CLAUDE.md
.claude
